OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F356A1780063875
OL,3,CCars covered in manure after parking
OL,4,Con Lake District farmer's field
OL,6,FDrivers who parked their cars on a
OL,7,Ffarmer's land in the Lake District
OL,8,Freturned to find their vehicles had
OL,9,Fbeen covered in suspected manure.
OL,11,FCumbria Police says that reports were
OL,12,Fmade on Tuesday about cars that had
OL,13,Fbeen been sprayed with what appeared
OL,14,Fto be cow slurry at a site near Rydal.
OL,16,FPhotos posted to social media by
OL,17,Fholidaymakers and locals showed dozens
OL,18,Fof cars covered in muck, with many
OL,19,Fdriving to the local car wash.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G1/5
