FL,357,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F356A1780063875
OL,3,CCars covered in manure after parking
OL,4,Con Lake District farmer's field
OL,6,FA worker at the garage in which the
OL,7,Fcar wash is situated refused to
OL,8,Fcomment but did confirm the car wash
OL,9,Fwas busy on Tuesday.
OL,11,FRemnants of the slurry could also be
OL,12,Fseen on surrounding sign posts -
OL,13,Fincluding one directing pedestrians
OL,14,Fand cyclists towards Ambleside.
OL,16,FThe land where the cars were parked
OL,17,Fsports 'no parking' signs at its
OL,18,Fentrance, including one which reads:
OL,19,F"Polite Notice - DO NOT PARK IN THE
OL,20,FFIELD".
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G2/5
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,357,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F356A1780063875
OL,3,CCars covered in manure after parking
OL,4,Con Lake District farmer's field
OL,6,FLarge stones had also been placed
OL,7,Falong the road into the land,
OL,8,Fseemingly to stop cars from driving
OL,9,Fonto the grass.
OL,11,FCumbria Police said: "Police were made
OL,12,Faware at 10pm on the 25 May of reports
OL,13,Fof cars having been sprayed with
OL,14,Fsuspected cow slurry at a location
OL,15,Fnear to Rydal.
OL,17,F"Our Neighbourhood Policing Teams are
OL,18,Fcarrying out further enquiries to
OL,19,Fdetermine the full circumstances."
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G3/5
