PN,35604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F356A1780063875
OL,3,CCars covered in manure after parking
OL,4,Con Lake District farmer's field
OL,6,FIt appeared that some of those who
OL,7,Fparked on the land had also left
OL,8,Flitter at the scene.
OL,10,FOne person commented: "Serves them
OL,11,Fright for being so entitled, farmer
OL,12,Fmight set a trend off here!"
OL,14,FAnother said: "They aren't visitors,
OL,15,Fthey are uneducated intruders. Stay
OL,16,Faway from places that deserve respect."
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G4/5
